config.cookingforblockheads.allowVeryToa: [待翻译] Toasting toasted bread again will turn into charcoal (only if no other mod adding toast is present). Set to false to disable.
config.cookingforblockheads.compressedCo: [待翻译] Compressed Cow in a Jar Milk Multiplier
[待翻译] Ex Compressum compatibility. Multiplier applied to the milk per tick for Compressed Cow in a Jar.
config.cookingforblockheads.cowJarEnable: [待翻译] Enable Cow in a Jar
[待翻译] If true, a cow can be squished into a Milk Jar by dropping an anvil on top.
config.cookingforblockheads.cowJarMilkPe: [待翻译] Milk Generation per Tick in Jar
[待翻译] The amount of milk the cow in a jar generates per tick.
config.cookingforblockheads.disallowOven: [待翻译] Set this to true if you'd like to disallow automation of the oven (pipes and such won't be able to insert/extract)
config.cookingforblockheads.largeCounter: [待翻译] Enabling this will make the kitchen counters have twice as much inventory space.
config.cookingforblockheads.ovenCookTime: [待翻译] The cooking time multiplier for the cooking oven. Higher values means it will take longer.
config.cookingforblockheads.ovenFuelTime: [待翻译] The fuel multiplier for the cooking oven. Higher values means fuel lasts longer, 1.0 is furnace default.
config.cookingforblockheads.ovenRequires: [待翻译] Set this to true if you'd like the oven to only accept cooking oil as fuel (requires Pam's Harvestcraft)
config.cookingforblockheads.showIngredie: [待翻译] Set to false if you don't want ingredients to be marked with a special icon in the recipe book.
config.cookingforblockheads.sinkRequires: [待翻译] Set this to true if you'd like the sink to require water to be piped in, instead of providing infinite of it.
container.cookingforblockheads.cow_jar_c: [待翻译] Compressed Cow in a Jar
tooltip.cookingforblockheads:very_toaste: [待翻译] Very Toasted Bread (do not eat)
